50 TEST(PioneerConfig, FileParser)
51 {
52  PioneerConfig con;
53  string package_path(PACKAGE_PATH);
54  string open_path(package_path);
55  open_path.append("/config/params/p3dx.p");
56  con.loadFile(open_path);
57  bool holonomic = con.getBool("General/Holonomic");
58  EXPECT_EQ(holonomic, true);
59  int max_vel = con.getInt("General/MaxVelocity");
60  EXPECT_EQ(max_vel, 2200);
61  double grlr = con.getDouble("General/RobotLengthRear");
62  EXPECT_FLOAT_EQ(grlr, 301.0);
63  string v7va = con.getString("Video 7/VideoAddress");
64  EXPECT_STREQ(v7va.c_str(), "192.168.0.90");
65  vector<int> sonar_0 = con.getIntVector("Sonar/SonarUnit 0");
66  EXPECT_EQ(sonar_0.size(), 9);
67  EXPECT_EQ(sonar_0[0], 69);
68 }
69 
70 TEST(PioneerConfig, Setters)
71 {
72  PioneerConfig con;
73  con.setBool("First Test", true);
74  EXPECT_EQ(con.getBool("First Test"), true);
75  con.setInt("Second Test", 22);
76  EXPECT_EQ(con.getInt("Second Test"), 22);
77  con.setDouble("Third Test", 23.8556481);
78  EXPECT_FLOAT_EQ(con.getDouble("Third Test"), 23.8556481);
79  std::vector<int> final_test(3, 100);
80  con.setIntVector("Fourth Test", final_test);
81  std::vector<int> out = con.getIntVector("Fourth Test");
82 
83  for (int i = 0; i < 3; ++i) {
84  EXPECT_EQ(out[i], 100);
85  }
86 }
